  <sect2 role="package">
    <title>Introduo a libkdcraw</title>

    <para>
      <application>Libkdcraw</application> is a KDE wrapper around the <xref
linkend="libraw"/> library for manipulating image metadata.
    </para>

    &lfs113_checked;

